<div class="title">Relaxing Free Association</div>
<div class="substance">Alprazolam (Xanax) & Cannabis</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=Sigea&Exact=1">Sigea</a></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; Sigea. "Relaxing Free Association: An Experience with Alprazolam (Xanax) & Cannabis (exp8697)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. May 12, 2004. erowid.org/exp/8697</div>

<br/>



